  personSpokenTo: {fileID: 11400000, guid: b2bdc4a268c1abc4386e1f154d6bd7e5, type: 2}
  delayBetweenMessages: 0
  lines:
  - Dear Citizen
  - Thank you for your efforts working remotely in helping evacuate other citizens.
  - As of tonight, all other citizens are expected to be evacuated.
  - All individuals including yourself working to evacuate citizens are to be privately
    evacuated beginning tomorrow morning.
  - Please await instructions on how this will be commenced expected to be delivered
    tomorrow morning.
